    // ─── Strategic Replan ───
    /**
     * Replace the entire strategic goal in a plan with a new one generated by the LLM.
     * Useful when the current strategic direction needs a fundamental change.
     *
     * @param plan - The current hierarchical plan (mutated in place)
     * @param newGoal - The new high-level goal description
     * @param llmClient - BYOK LLM client for strategic re-planning
     * @returns The updated plan with new strategic goal, tactical tasks, and metadata
