 * Uses `nomic-embed-text` model by default (768-dim).
 * Falls back to TF-IDF bag-of-words (256-dim) if Ollama is unavailable.
 *
 * @example
 * ```ts
 * const provider = new OllamaEmbeddingProvider();
 * const [[v]] = await provider.embed(["hello world"]);
 * ```
 */
